BUG-001 — Username Login is Case-Insensitive

FieldDetailSeverityMediumPriorityMediumModuleLogin / SecurityTC ReferenceTC_008EnvironmentChrome 124 / Windows 11

Steps to Reproduce


Navigate to https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com
Enter Username: ADMIN (all caps)
Enter Password: admin123
Click Login


Expected Result
Login fails with error: "Invalid credentials". Username should be case-sensitive.

Actual Result
Login succeeds with username "ADMIN" (all caps). System is NOT case-sensitive for the username field. No error message displayed.

Reference: NFR-S01 — Authentication Security

